title: Top and Jungle Main Looking For OOL Team
body: Hello guys, I am a Gold player, been playing for a fair while, and am looking for a team to participate in the OOL tournament. Very reliable and if the people im playing with are better, I can easily adapt and am always eager to learn from those. IGN: Conzeyaus
